stimulus:
By accepting to participate in this study, you confirm:

- That I have carefully read the explanations regarding this study and the entire experimental procedure;
- That I have been informed about the aims and objectives of this research;
- That I am aware of the inconveniences, if any, caused by the experiment;
- That I have received satisfactory assurances regarding the confidentiality of the information obtained from the examination of my own person;
- That I am aware that I can withdraw at any stage of the study.

Press [Y] to accept.
Press [N] to refuse.
